\r\n；致重傷者，處3年以上10年以下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCDM/110%2c%e4%b8%ad%e7%b0%a1%2c2215%2c20211020%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCDM,110,中簡,2215,20211020,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"中簡","JNO":"2215","JDATE":"20211020","JTITLE":"傷害"}